Rubie Charles JENKINS v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 3406. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Nov. 12, 1946. C. Arthur Anderson, of St. Louis, Mo., for appellant. Charles E. Dierker, U. S. Atty., and Robert E. Shelton, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, BRATTON, HUX--MAN, and MURRAH, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed November 12, 1946, for :failure to prosecute.
